description:
One of Europe's most celebrated actresses, Carice van Houten is best known as 'Melisandre' in the iconic TV show Game of Thrones, a powerful performance that earned her an Emmy nomination. Watch as she converses with Sadhguru about the Save Soil movement.

#SaveSoil #Sadhguru  savesoil.org/live
